These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, blue, white, lavender
There 4 different types of food: apple, asparagus, corn, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, funk, hip-hop, house
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, spy, crime, family
 1. the fan house is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 3. the person who likes amber is not the person watching spy movies##6
 4. the fan hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan funk##3
 5. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the fan house##5
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
 7. the fan disco is the person who likes amber##1
 8. the person who likes amber is between the person watching crime movies and the person eating apple##2
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
10. the person watching family movies is not the person eating asparagus##6
11. the person who likes blue is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan house is in an odd position##4
13. the person who likes white is the fan house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | white     | amber      | lavender      | blue    |
| Food          | apple    | asparagus | strawberry | corn     |
| Music-Genre   | house    | disco     | hip-hop    | funk     |
| Nationality   | family | animation | crime    | spy |

