.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-2::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, cat, hamster
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, reading, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, punk, soul
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, go, bridge
 1. the person playing go is the owner of the bird##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
 5. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the fan blues and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 7. the fan blues is on the right of the person playing go##1
 8. the fan soul is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
10. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
11. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
12. the fan blues is not the person playing go##6
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the fan blues##1
14. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the fan punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food          | cat    | hedgehog | bird | hamster       |
| Hobby         | traveling | puzzles   | drawing  | reading       |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | hip-hop   | punk     | blues         |
| Sport         | domino   | canasta   | go | bridge |

