 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person eating pumpkin##2
 3. the person watching spy movies is the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the dannemann-smoker##6
 5. the person watching spy movies is the fonseca-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
 7. the person watching spy movies is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
 8. the person eating spinach is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
 9. the chaman-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
12. the chaman-smoker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
13. the person watching fantasy movies is the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |
