 3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person who growspoppy##6
 5. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 6. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
10. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
13. the person driving the bike is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
14. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3

.:: Answer ::.
