.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-18::.
4 different games are played: chess, whist, billiard, bridge
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, emerald, black, aquamarine
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, colombian, french
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, rat
 1. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 2. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the chinchilla and the australian##2
 3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
 4. the owner of the rat is the person who likes emerald##1
 5. the french is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 7. the person playing chess is not the colombian##6
 8. the person playing billiard is the french##1
 9. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
10. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who likes brown##1
12. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
13. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage      | bridge    | chess  | whist          | billiard |
| Job           | emerald | aquamarine | black | brown    |
| Nationality   | colombian | australian   | brazilian     | french        |
| Pet           | rat       | cat          | dog           | chinchilla    |

