.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-20::.
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, poker, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, mystery, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, malaysian, thai
City: london, colone, san-francisco, new-york
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the american##1
 3. the person playing domino is not the person watching disaster movies##6
 4. the american is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the malaysian is not the person playing domino##6
10. the person playing domino is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
11. the person playing poker is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | bridge | mah-jongg  | poker     | domino     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | drama      | disaster   | satire     |
| Nationality   | canadian  | american   | malaysian  | thai       |
| Transport     | colone   | london | san-francisco | new-york |

 